See you there! ❤️

To enter:
📸 Snap a picture of JonnyPops Organic Freezer Pops at your local Costco store (No purchase necessary!)
📱 Share your picture of the Organic Freezer Pops found at Costco to your story and tag @jonnypops!

Happy searching, be sure to check the juice aisle, the snack aisle, and near the freezer section! 😉 

Giveaway ends Sunday, July 6th at 5pm CT. Winners will be DM'd by @jonnypops to get their shipping information. This giveaway is in no way sponsored, endorsed, administered by or associated with Instagram. Giveaway is open to US residents only. Good luck!
